How to update/create translation
-------------------------
Update translation strings via lupdate (lupdate-qt4).
If you're adding new language, add it into CMakeLists.txt

 # lupdate .. -ts qdevkit_${lang}.ts # substitute lang for "cs", "sk" etc.

Add translation strings
-----------------------
Use Qt Linguist for editing .ts files.

 # linguist qdevkit_${lang}.ts

